Steps to install the ICD database:
1) Copy the zipped ICD database files into this directory available from

	ICD9

	http://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/ICD9ProviderDiagnosticCodes/Downloads/cmsv29_master_descriptions.zip

	ICD10

   	https://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/ICD10/Downloads/DiagnosisGEMs_2012.zip
	https://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/ICD10/Downloads/ProcedureGEMs_2012.zip
	https://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/ICD10/Downloads/ReimbursementMapping_2012.zip
	https://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/ICD10/Downloads/2012_PCS_long_and_abbreviated_titles.zip
	https://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/ICD10/Downloads/ICD10OrderFiles_2012.zip

2) In OpenEMR, go to Administration->Other->ICD in order to then install/upgrade
   the ICD database.

